AB Volvo is issuing a 70 billioneurolire bond due May 31, 1990 paying 10-1/8 pct and priced at100-1/2 pct, lead manager Banca Commerciale Italiana said.    The bond is available in denominations of two mln lire andwill be listed in London.    Fees comprise 7/8 pct selling concession with 1/2 pct formanagement and underwriting combined.    Payment date is April 24 and there will be a long firstcoupon. REUTER&#3;